# Operator-only social posting schedule / home-office window policy: keep under docs/private/ (e.g. social_drafts/OPERATOR_SOCIAL_POSTING_WINDOWS.pt_BR.md) — never copy full tables to public tracked docs.
docs/private/
.cursor/private/

